<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_241" id="120v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_241_r1l1"><expan>Berchtold<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ʒugenreẅt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_241_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Berchtold als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt vvıe eẅch geſagt ſey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r1l3">Daʒ Jr gen vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſagt</expan> ſüllt ſein . daʒ Jr bey der nom geweſt ſüllt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r1l4">ſeın . dıe vns vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> von <expan>frıcʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vom Eglofſteın von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r1l5">Nıkel <expan>lang<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd Jren <expan>helff<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>geſcheh<ex>en</ex></expan> ſein . Des Jr vnſchuldıg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r1l6">ſeyt etc . das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r1l7">dıe dıe ſache antrıft . kein klag noch red gehört daʒ ſıe eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r1l8"><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> in <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dechtnuſſ</expan> gehabt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Alſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır eẅch von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r1l9">der ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> keins argen <expan>gewarte<ex>n</ex></expan> . Vnd <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu dıſen <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r1l10">mıt eẅch niht ʒu <expan>ſchıke<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . denn gut . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r1l11">Martinj </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_241" id="120v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Berchtold<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Zugenrewt<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Berchtold, als ir uns
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ewch gesagt sey, daz
                        ir gen uns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sagt</expan> süllt sein, daz ir bey der nom
                        gewest süllt sein, die uns und den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> von
                                <expan>Fricze<ex>n</ex></expan> vom Eglofstein von Nikel
                                <expan>Lang<ex>en</ex></expan> und iren
                            <expan>helff<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gescheh<ex>en</ex></expan> sein, des ir unschuldig seyt etc., das
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von
                        den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, die die sache antrift, kein klag noch
                        red gehört, daz sie ewch <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> in
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dechtnuss</expan> gehabt
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n;</expan> also <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        ewch von der sache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> keins argen
                                <expan>gewarte<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        zu disen <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> mit ewch niht zu
                                <expan>schike<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> denn gut. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Martini. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
